*gentoo-vdr-scripts-2.7.5 (03 May 2016)

  03 May 2016; Joerg Bornkessel <hd_brummy@gentoo.org>
  +gentoo-vdr-scripts-2.7.5.ebuild:
  eapi6; add support ionice, suggested by T.Loescher

  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.28

  05 May 2016; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org>
  gentoo-vdr-scripts-2.7.5.ebuild:
  Fix DOCS expansion

  Delay DOCS expansion until src_install(). It is meaningless in global
  scope since it happens in arbitrary directory which will not have
  README* files. Furthermore, it triggers verbose failure due to failglob.

  15 May 2016; Joerg Bornkessel <hd_brummy@gentoo.org>
  gentoo-vdr-scripts-2.7.5.ebuild:
  removed useless inherit eutils for eapi=6; removed useless src_prepare part

  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.28

